eader"><h3>主办方</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/topic/19793502" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='t$t$19793502'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1003bb2fb402f1b21f60b7d5ca555b71_l.jpg" alt="知乎圆桌" class="avatar d50"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/topic/19793502" class="name" data-hovercard='t$t$19793502'>知乎圆桌</a><div class="bio">举办过 255 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description">知乎发起的在线嘉宾讨论，详情请点击：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/20886632" data-editable="true" data-title="什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与" class="">什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与</a>？<br>圆桌页面：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable" data-editable="true" data-title="活动">活动列表</a></p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/rayche" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$rayche'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ee358355fc7784e5d59ba504ffefcd19_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="车尔尼雷夫司机"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/feixingyuan/rayche/answers" class="answers text-muted">11 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/rayche" data-hovercard='p$t$rayche'>车尔尼雷夫司机</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span><div class="bio">航空公司 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 飞行员</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/pasco-sir-14" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$pasco-sir-14'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/b8f68cc57fc4e0f8d02a694ff6b5b69a_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="Sir Pasco"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/feixingyuan/pasco-sir-14/answers" class="answers text-muted">5 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/pasco-sir-14" data-hovercard='p$t$pasco-sir-14'>Sir Pasco</a><span class="icon icon-badge